{"vv13:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv13:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv13:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv13:0.4":"13. Pathamasunisavimanavatthu ","vv13:1.1":"“Abhikkantena vannena, ","vv13:1.2":"ya tvam titthasi devate; ","vv13:1.3":"Obhasenti disa sabba, ","vv13:1.4":"osadhi viya taraka. ","vv13:2.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv13:2.2":"kena te idha mijjhati; ","vv13:2.3":"Uppajjanti ca te bhoga, ","vv13:2.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv13:3.1":"Pucchami tam devi mahanubhave, ","vv13:3.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv13:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv13:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv13:4.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv13:4.2":"moggallanena pucchita; ","vv13:4.3":"Panham puttha viyakasi, ","vv13:4.4":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv13:5.1":"“Aham manussesu manussabhuta, ","vv13:5.2":"Sunisa ahosim sasurassa gehe. ","vv13:6.1":"Addasam virajam bhikkhum, ","vv13:6.2":"vippasannamanavilam; ","vv13:6.3":"Tassa adasaham puvam, ","vv13:6.4":"pasanna sehi panibhi; ","vv13:6.5":"Bhagaddhabhagam datvana, ","vv13:6.6":"modami nandane vane. ","vv13:7.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv13:7.2":"tena me idha mijjhati; ","vv13:7.3":"Uppajjanti ca me bhoga, ","vv13:7.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv13:8.1":"Akkhami te bhikkhu mahanubhava, ","vv13:8.2":"Manussabhuta yamakasi punnam; ","vv13:8.3":"Tenamhi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv13:8.4":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv13:9.1":"Pathamasunisavimanam terasamam. "}